data.title: Membership & Fees
data.meta_description: We have loyal and friendly members who are open and welcoming to all. We have membership packages to suit all ages and abilities.
data.text:
Here at Horam Park Golf Club we have loyal and friendly members who are open and welcoming to all.

We have a number of membership packages to suit all ages and abilities. Please see below for details on our:

Club Membership

Golf Academy Membership

Course Fees

Golf Academy Membership

Check With Our Club Professional For New Upcoming Dates.

The 6 month Academy Membership includes:

*5 x Individual 30 minute Golf Lessons

*6 x 1 Hour Monthly Group Lessons

*7 x 9 Holes of Golf (20% Discounted Green Fees thereafter)

*Members Rates For Driving Range

*Shop Discounts/Equipment advice from the Pros

*Bar/Restaurant Membership Discount Card

*Bring up to 3 guests with you for members guest rates green fees

*Invite to Graduate Membership after completion

Come and begin your golfing career, or improve upon your existing game with our friendly and experienced PGA Golf Professionals.
